    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/charles_bass_241128",
        "quote": "The U.S. government knew that China wanted to acquire sensitive U.S. technology, and instead of implementing a policy to prevent them from acquiring the information, the government all but gave them an invitation to take our equipment and designs.",
